  "description": "<p>This is NOT:<br />❌ A desk job<br />❌ A boring environment <br />❌ A “wait 3 years for promotion” job</p><p>This IS:<br />✔ People-facing<br />✔ Energy-based<br />✔ Paid by performance</p><p><strong>Your Role</strong></p><ul><li><p>Sell & promote brands face-to-face</p></li><li><p>Recruit people who match the vibe</p></li><li><p>Train & lead your own team</p></li><li><p>Build income + leadership skills</p></li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li><p>💰 Unlimited commission</p></li><li><p>🔥 Fun team culture</p></li><li><p>📈 Fast promotions</p></li><li><p>🎓 Sales & people training</p></li></ul><p>If you need a chair to feel productive — this isn’t for you.<br /></p><p><strong>APPLY NOW! </strong><br /><strong>Whatsapp: Mak - 81714219</strong></p>",
